# c3) Funkce pro zznam vsledk rznch kombinac parametr pro dan model v podob DataFrame
def record_results(results, model_name):
    records = []
    for param, mean_score in zip(results["params"], results["mean_test_score"]):
        # pidvn novch kl (mean_accuracy a model strojovho uen)
        param.update({"mean_accuracy": mean_score, "model": model_name})
        # pidavn hodnot do records
        records.append(param)
    return records

In[24]:
# b1) Flat clustering
# c1) Zkouen rznch hodnot pro poet shluk u K-means a vpoet silhouette skre
kmeans_results = []
# a1) poet shluk od 2 do 9 (experimentovn s rznmi nastaven shlukovn)
for n_clusters in range(2, 10):
    kmeans = KMeans(n_clusters=n_clusters, random_state=42, n_init=10)
    # provdn shlukovn dat a piazen datovch bod k jednotlivm shlukm pomoc Kmeans
    labels = kmeans.fit_predict(X_scaled)
    # vpoet silhouette_score
    # silhouette skre (interval <-1;1>) -> hodnocen kvality shlukovn, m vy, tm lep definovan shluky
    silhouette_avg = silhouette_score(X_scaled, labels)
    kmeans_results.append((n_clusters, silhouette_avg))
    # Zobrazen dan silhouette skre pro dan poet shluk
    print(f"\nFlat clustering: Poet shluk: {n_clusters}, Silhouette skre: {silhouette_avg:.4f}")

# b2) Hierarchical clustering
# c2) Zkouen rznch hodnot pro poet shluk u K-means a vpoet silhouette skre
agglo_results = []
# a1) poet shluk od 2 do 9 (experimentovn s rznmi nastaven shlukovn)
for n_clusters in range(2, 10):
    agglo = AgglomerativeClustering(n_clusters=n_clusters)
    # provdn shlukovn dat a piazen datovch bod k jednotlivm shlukm pomoc Agglomerative Clustering
    labels = agglo.fit_predict(X_scaled)
    # vpoet silhouette_score
    silhouette_avg = silhouette_score(X_scaled, labels)
    agglo_results.append((n_clusters, silhouette_avg))
    # Zobrazen dan silhouette skre pro dan poet shluk
    # silhouette skre (interval <-1;1>) -> hodnocen kvality shlukovn, m vy, tm lep definovan shluky
    print(f"\nHierarchical clustering: Poet shluk: {n_clusters}, Silhouette skre: {silhouette_avg:.4f}")

# c) Kombinace matice nklad s matic zmn
# Vytvoen matice nklad
cost_matrix = np.array([[0, 10], [1, 0]])
# Vypotn matice zmn pro modely random forrest a decision tree
conf_matrix_dt = confusion_matrix(y_test, y_pred_dt)
conf_matrix_rf = confusion_matrix(y_test, y_pred_rf)
# Vypotn celkovch nklad random forrest a decisn tree
total_cost_dt = np.sum(cost_matrix * conf_matrix_dt)
total_cost_rf = np.sum(cost_matrix * conf_matrix_rf)
 
print("Total cost Decision Tree:", total_cost_dt)
print("Total cost Random Forest:", total_cost_rf)
# Pro minimalizaci nklad by ml bt preferovn Random Forest, protoe jeho celkov nklady (241) jsou ni ne u Decision Tree (255).

Total cost Random Forest: 241
In[34]:
# d) Optimalizace prahov hodnoty (threshold) na zklad nklad

# Vypotn pravdpodobnosti, e instance pat do tdy "1" (pozitivn tda), pomoc modelu nhodnho lesa.
probabilities = rf_model.predict_proba(X_test_scaled)[:, 1]
# Vytvoen seznamu monch hodnot prah klasifikace
thresholds = np.arange(0.1, 1.0, 0.1)
# Inicializace promnn pro nejlep prh klasifikace, kter bude aktualizovna pozdji
best_threshold = 0
# Nastaven poten hodnoty minimlnch nklad na nekoneno (umouje hledn minimlnch nklad pi testovn rznch prah)
min_total_cost = float('inf')
In[35]:
# Pevod y_test na seln hodnoty (0 = tested_negative, 1 = tested_positive)
y_test_numeric = y_test.apply(lambda x: 1 if x == 'tested_positive' else 0)
In[36]:
# Vytvoen cost_matrix
cost_matrix = np.array([[0, 1],  # Nklady pro predikce 0 a 1
                        [5, 0]])  # Nklady pro predikce 1 a 0
In[37]:
for threshold in thresholds:
# Predikce na zklad prahu
    y_pred_threshold = (probabilities >= threshold).astype(int)
In[38]:
 # Vytvoen matice zmn pro zadan prh
conf_matrix_threshold = confusion_matrix(y_test_numeric, y_pred_threshold)
In[39]:
# Vpoet celkovch nklad
total_cost = np.sum(cost_matrix * conf_matrix_threshold)
In[40]:
# Kontrola, zda tento prh m ni nklady
if total_cost < min_total_cost:
        min_total_cost = total_cost
        best_threshold = threshold
 
print("Best threshold:", best_threshold, "with minimum cost:", min_total_cost)

# Z hlediska minimalizace nklad je Random Forest lep ne Decision Tree, protoe m ni celkov nklady (241 oproti 255).

Best threshold: 0.9 with minimum cost: 266

wcss = []
# Vytvoen seznamu hodnot pro poet shluk k
k_values = range(1, 11)
# Smyka, kter prochz vechny hodnoty potu shluk k
for k in k_values:
    kmeans = KMeans(n_clusters=k, random_state=42, n_init=10)
    kmeans.fit(X)
    wcss.append(kmeans.inertia_)

plt.ylabel('WCSS')
plt.title('Elbow Method for optimal k')

In[48]:
# Testovn rznch maximlnch hloubek stromu (1 a 20)
depths = range(1, 21)
f1_scores = []  # F1 skre pro kadou hloubku 

for depth in depths:
    clf = DecisionTreeClassifier(max_depth=depth, random_state=42)
    clf.fit(X_train, y_train)  # Trnink stromu na trnovac mnoin
    y_pred = clf.predict(X_test)  # Predikce na testovac mnoin
    f1_scores.append(f1_score(y_test, y_pred))  # Vpoet F1 skre

# Najdeme hloubku stromu s nejlepm F1 skre
best_depth = depths[np.argmax(f1_scores)]

# Trnink rozhodovacho stromu s nejlep hloubkou
clf_final = DecisionTreeClassifier(max_depth=best_depth, random_state=42)
clf_final.fit(X_train, y_train)

# Vizualizace rozhodovacho stromu
plt.figure(figsize=(30, 10)) # Nastaven velikosti grafu
plot_tree(
    clf_final,
    filled=True, # Barevn vyplnn uzl
    feature_names=X.columns.tolist(),  # Jmna atribut
    class_names=label_encoder.classes_.tolist(),  # Jmna td
    rounded=True, # Zaoblen rohy uzl
    fontsize=10 # Velikost psma
)
plt.title('Optimalizovan rozhodovac strom')
plt.show()
